    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You curse a bleeding opponent with uncertainty.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Int 13, Use Magic Device 5 ranks.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />As a standard action, you can curse an enemy you've damaged with a melee attack in the last minute to become hesitant. The target must succeed at a Reflex save or take a -10 penalty on any initiative check it makes in the next minute.<br /><br /><strong>Special</strong><br />If a shaman or witch uses this blood hex, the target is unable to take a full-attack action for 1 round. This effect can be extended with the cackle hex.</p>",
